perf: Error, one of the following options is required, --install|--start|--stop|--postprocess

The following options are available:

	--install                 verify this perf tool will work

	--start|stop|postprocess  start/stop/postprocess the data collection
	-d str|--dir=str          directory to store data collection (required)
	-r str|--record-opts=str  options one would use to record perf data (optional, default: '-a --freq=100)'
	-p str|--report-opts=str  options one would use to report perf data (optional, default: '--show-nr-samples -I)'
	--callgraph               generate a call graph by adding '-g' to the record and report options

	-h|--help                 display this help message
